
nginx with php

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5eB-MtdFXlI


install git - sudo apt-get install git


update the pi firmware with rpi-update

sort distorted audio
 (not with USB high speed; add dwc_otg.speed=1 to /boot/cmdline.txt, but that will slow down all USB transfers)

cd into /var/www/
git clone https://github.com/danbuntu/MPD_frontend_for_Raspberry_PI.git
sudo nano /etc/nginx/sites-available/default
edit the root to be:  root /var/www/MPD_frontend_for_Raspberry_PI;


setup mpd

http://lesbonscomptes.com/pages/raspmpd.html



midori at startup
http://www.niteoweb.com/blog/raspberry-pi-boot-to-browser

